metadata.name: Koryusai x Ghost in the Shell
metadata.description:
Koryusai x GITS

Artwork by Mannay (2022)

————————————————————

This illustration is inspired by an Isoda Koryusai ukiyo-e from 1773-1775 as well as Motoko, the main character from the anime Ghost in the Shell.

Digitized using Photoshop.
————————————————————

Artwork size : 3000 × 4559 px
